Global Partners LP Completes Acquisition of Four Liquid Energy Terminals from Gulf Oil

Global strengthens operations in the Northeast and continues to expand its terminal network WALTHAM, Mass.–(BUSINESS WIRE)– Global Partners LP (NYSE: GLP) (“Global” or the “Partnership”) announced today the successful closing of its acquisition of four liquid energy terminals from Gulf Oil Limited Partnership (“Gulf Oil”). The terminals are strategically located in Chelsea, MA, New Haven, CT,… Read More »

Global Partners Named to Fortune 2024 World’s Most Admired Companies List

Fortune Magazine has named Global Partners to its 2024 list of the World’s Most Admired Companies.
